          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>That time of the year is almost here when the familiar scent of modaks is steaming in the kitchen, the sound of aarti rejoices everyone, the doors are open and laughter echoes through every home. Every year, Ganesh Chaturthi brings us closer. Whether you are the host or visiting homes, Ganpati is the time when you want to dress to celebrate the tradition, the emotion and the beauty of Lord Ganesha’s festival. For Ganpati 2025, why not celebrate with jewelry that reflects exactly that? </p><p>As more people embrace ecofriendly idols of Lord Ganesha, more heads are also turning towards the sustainability and the sparkle of Lab Grown Diamonds. Along with sparkle, Lab Grown Diamond Jewellery is also a conscious choice. Let’s explore the must-have pieces of Lab Grown Diamond Jewellery perfect to reflect the brilliance, blessings and beginnings that Ganesh Chaturthi brings.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
